<promed@promedmail.org>
[Primorski Krai (region) is in far east Russia along the Sea of Japan. It
borders China on the south, southwest, the west and northwest. In the
north, it borders the Khabarovsk region and in the extreme south, the
Democratic Republic of Korea. The total area of the region is 165 900
square km., and the population is 2 071 200. - Mod.NP]
[It may be assumed that the eradication of this outbreak requires special
efforts, particularly in view of the distance from laboratories and
centers, and the complex border situation. An official update from the
Russian veterinary services is long overdue. - Mod.AS]
